FBIS4-36101 "drnes109_a_94005" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Further Details Provided Further Details Provided LD0606224994 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 2200 GMT 6 Jun 94 LD0606224994 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Excerpts] In another statement the security services announced that 75 members of a terrorist network were arrested by the security forces after investigations begun about two months ago. Most of the members of this gang moved about using forged identity cards, and it is claimed that they belong to the Armed Islamic Group of Said Mekhlouf, the same source said. [passage omitted: gang specialized in various crimes, areas where it was active] The gang used stolen money to buy houses that were used as hideouts in various areas of the country, the same source said.
